      "comment": "STARSTRUCK (2) was safely held on debut after settling well back when sixth (22.60) at this track over 390m. Much improved and can open winning account. MAYWYN OBAMA (1) gets a chance to turn around his from the inside. Last time finished last over 520m at Q Parklands beaten 18 lengths (31.45) behind Remember Bruce in a Maiden on May 3. The form from his last run stacks up well. Can do much better this time. FROG'S ROCK (3) shows ability but remains a maiden after eight starts. Is better than last start when out of the placings, finishing third (20.64) at Capalaba. Must be included in calculations. SISTER HOLLY (8) should be thereabouts.",
